& [Mechanism_002_SpecialGeometry] is a table row
  + [mechanism] is special variety geometry, products, abelian variety structures, or reductions to known cases
  + [input_anchor] is Hodge class in a variety with extra geometric structure
  + [cycle_output] is special-case algebraic cycles
  + [construction_strength] is special_case
  + [known_boundary] is known_case_or_open_by_family
