  + [next_question] is identify which special geometry could provide the missing cycle source

& [Mechanism_003_NormalFunctionsVariation] is a table row
  + [mechanism] is normal functions, variations of Hodge structure, and family methods
  + [input_anchor] is moving Hodge-theoretic data in a family
  + [cycle_output] is sometimes cycle detection or obstruction data rather than direct cycles
